data.description: Welcome Home to your beautifully renovated townhouse in the Katonah school district. Light and bright end unit has been fully renovated in every room from the bamboo engineering waterproof flooring to the marble tile, you will be pleasantly surprised with the detail and love that went into this transformation. As you walk in from the new trex decking, you will be welcomed with cathedral ceilings in the living room. Off to the left is the formal dining room. The eat-in kitchen was fully upgraded in 2018 w/new cabinets, countertops, appliances and backsplash. As you walk up to the first level, there is the secondary bedroom with plenty of closet space as well as a full en-suite bathroom. Up a couple of stairs you will find the primary suite which includes 2 custom walk-in closets. The primary bathroom was fully renovated with marble tile, double marble vanity, modern toilet, LED mirror, shelving, glass shower enclosure, shower faucet with jets, a hugh rain shower head, and a fan. Off the primary suite is a spiral staircase leading up to a loft that adds additional living space for an office/den/play area. The laundry room is in the partially finished basement. There is storage under the stairs in the garage. Garage can fit one car.
